Title: Idol temperature change nail polish 10 ml(yellow)
Description: Beautiful effect with changing its color with change in temperature. If the temperature is less then 25, the polish will change to light colour and if the temperature is more than 25, it will change to dark colour.You can run hot or cold water over the polish to check the effect instantly. Its perfect for parties, any occasions or daily wear as well.This polish can be used as daily wear or as base colour for any kind of nail art such as, stamping, free hand, dotting mani or nail rhinestones or studs. Title: SOS Digital Ultrasonic 9 Program Tens Therapy Unit Electrotherapy Device
Description: Ultrasound is applied using a transducer or applicator that is in direct contact with the patient's skin. Gel is used on all surfaces of the head to reduce friction and assist transmission of the ultrasonic waves. Therapeutic ultrasound in physical therapy is alternating compression and rarefaction of sound waves with measured frequency to Maximum energy absorption in soft tissue occurs from 2 to 5 cm. Intensity decreases as the waves penetrate deeper. They are absorbed primarily by connective tissue: ligaments, tendons, and fascia and also by scar tissue or spasm.Conditions for which ultrasound may be used for treatment include the follow examples: ligament sprains, muscle strains, tendonitis, joint inflammation, plantar fasciitis, metatarsalgia, facet irritation, impingement syndrome, bursitis, rheumatoid arthritis, osteoarthritis, and scar tissue adhesion.

Simply fill it with hot water and stick it in your bed, under your blankets, about 10 minutes before you plan to hit the sack. Your sheets will be warm up in no time. 2. If you experience regular back pain then a hot water bottle is a really good investment for you. According to Lauri Grossman, DO, a licensed chiropractor and the founder of the Department of Homeopathic Medicine at New York University, using hot and cold therapy can help ease back pain. She explains “cold therapy (applied via an ice pack) works better for inflammation and helps to reduce swelling, while heat (via a hot water bottle) is ideal for reducing cramping and muscle spasms.” 3. While pain medications can work to alleviate menstrual cramps, try a more natural solution by applying heat to your lower abdomen with a hot water bottle. The heat has been said to relax the uterus, as well as reduce constriction of your blood vessels and improve blood flow to the uterus, all of which can help ease your cramps.

Title: Kent Super-Premium Real Cherrywood Pure Bristles Dressing
Description: Kent is a 230-Year-Old brand of premium brushes from the United Kingdom. Known for its legacy of producing the largest, widest, most premium and highest quality brushes, the company has a range spanning head to toe. Kent Super Premium series is the one of the finest ranges of Kent for the discerning few. All brushes in the super premium range are hand crafted, hand-finished and made with the choicest materials sourced from the best possible suppliers around the world. The hallmark of this series is the use of real bristle instead of conventional cheap plastic. Brushing hair is the simplest beauty treatment there is, easing tension and stress from the head and neck. Brushing with real bristle stimulates and encourages essential oils in the scalp to flow through the hair strands nourishing and protecting each hair strand, leaving it smooth and naturally shiny. Bristle strengths vary for fine or thick hair, and for best brushing performance it is important to use the right bristle strength. A bristle is similar to a hair in construction, and sections cut from nearer the root of the bristle are strongest and best for brushing thick hair, while sections from the tip or flag end are softer and more suited to fine hair and a delicate scalp. All brush designs in the Kent premium range are suitable for traditional brushing or blow drying. No effort has been spared. No corners have been cut in the craftsmanship and material used in the Kent Super premium series. This range is for the discerning few who prefer nothing but the very best in life.
CategoryName: Baby Care>Grooming>Hair Brushes

Title: Dove Dryness Care Conditioner(180 ml)
Description: Before conditioners were formulated, people used various oils to nourish their hair and keep it soft all the time.The secret behind oiling your hair is that it helps form a protective shield around your strands and also helps in keeping your hair soft through the day. Come explore the whole new range of hair care products from Dove that will feed your hair with the same nourishment as oil and ensure to completely transform and protect your hair. The Dove Dry Therapy Conditioner has been composed to condition dry hair so you can flaunt healthy and thick lustrous hair all the time. The special formula of sunflower seed oil and glycerin supplies moisture to your locks and ensures that each strand is silky and smooth after a wash. Damaged hair can be revived back to life with the special micro moisture serum that this conditioner is formulated with. Binding moisture and nourishment within your hair, this conditioner helps you to gain all the lost hydration and hence get healthy and strong hair. The conditioner also reduces split ends and smoothes frizzy hair so your dull hair is revived and looks beautiful all day long. The anti-static properties of this conditioner ensure that your hair is given a glossy final finish, so every hairdo is perfected. This natural and organic conditioner is a great addition to your bathroom so don’t delay making this decision.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Hair Care>Conditioners

Title: Dove Intense Repair Conditioner(170 ml)
Description: Styling damaged hair can be a nightmare for any woman, especially when she is getting dressed for a big event. But the solution is simple. Apply this Dove Intense Repair Conditioner after you shampoo your hair and then dry it, and style it with ease. Whether you want to pull your hair up in a bun or ponytail, or leave it loose to frame your face, you can do it with much more ease. With Keratin Actives To Nourish Your Hair With keratin actives, the conditioner gives damaged hair all the nourishment that it needs to be smooth and free of tangles and easier to style and maintain. Split ends and breakages are no longer problems you will have to face. Micro Moisture Serum Thanks to the micro moisture serum in this conditioner, your hair is now going to have more moisture to look more healthy and stylish.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Hair Care>Conditioners

Title: L'Oreal Paris Repairing Creambath Hair spa conditioner(490 g)
Description: Directions:Shampoo and towel dry.Mix one scoop of the creambath, with one vial of the selected scalp concentrate. Apply the mix with a brush to your scalp only. Take another scoop of cream bath only and work it to the mid-lengths and ends of the hair with your fingers.Now you need your little sister, mother or if you are lucky enough, your hubby to give you a nice and relaxing head massage. Post massage, wrap your head in a hot towel. Leave for 10 minutes or more. (If you are not already familiar with the hot towel method, it is quite easy. Just soak a towel in hot water, take the towel out and squeeze out the water completely, and then wrap it around your head for 5-10 minutes. It works as an alternative to steam.You can repeat this process if required. Remember to squeeze all the hot water out of the towel, you don’t want to damage your hair. You can even wrap your head in a hot towel after oiling , or after using a deep conditioning mask.)

Title: Roots Brown Wide Teeth Comb for Wavy/ Curly/ Thick/ Long Hair - Pack of 3
Description: The Roots Brown Combs Are Made From Cellulose (Plant Based Extract) Acetate, Which Helps Cut Down On Static Resulting In Lesser Frizz And Flyaways. This Material Also Makes These Combs Hypoallergenic Which Means They Are Skin Friendly And Will Not Cause Any Form Of Allergy On Any Skin Type. Moreover, The Combs Are Seamless, Which Means They Have Smoothened And Rounded Tips That Massage The Scalp And Stimulate The Natural Oils And Smoothened Teeth Edges To Prevent Scraping Of The Hair Cuticles And Scalp While Styling Dry/Wet Hair. Watch The Hair Behave And Stay In Place As You Witness A Comfortable And Irritation-Free Hair Combing Experience, With Every Stroke.Ordinary Combs have sharp edges that damage the cuticle, roughen the scales and cause unhealthy split hair. In fact, such combs actually undo treatments of even the best shampoos!Roots Combs have rounded teeth that massage the scalp and stimulate natural oils in the hair cuticle. This keeps scales smooth, so hair stays strong and healthy.Always and only use a Roots comb and hair brush. Title: Deve Herbes Pure Canola Oil - Pack Of Two (100ml + 100ml) Brassica Napus 100% Natural Cold Pressed
Description: Benefits of Canola Oil:Lower Cholesterol: Canola oil contains absolutely no cholesterol, which is a major benefit for those people who have struggled with cholesterol issues in the past, as well as the conditions that naturally come with high cholesterol. It can actually reduce your cholesterol levels by 10-15%.Skin Health: Canola oil, is rich in vitamin E. Vitamin E is very effective as an antioxidant, and is able to protect the skin from the damaging effects of free radicals. This can keep your skin supple and smooth, increase the healing rate of injuries, reduce the appearance of blemishes and acne marks, and slow down the appearance of wrinkles.Cell Membranes: Vitamin E is also a lipid-soluble antioxidant, meaning that it can help protect the integrity of cell membranes throughout the body.Energy Levels: The low amount of cholesterol and the high amount of important antioxidants can help the body’s metabolism move at a normal rate. Your body doesn’t become sluggish and your energy isn’t sapped by slow circulation or an overstressed cardiovascular system.Brain Function: The antioxidants that combat free radicals also prevent damage to the brain, which can shut down neural connections and lead to diseases like Alzheimer and dementia.Diabetes: Monounsaturated fats not only help to prevent heart disease, but they can also help to maintain glucose levels in the blood.Using canola oil on eczema, dry heals, elbows and blemishes can effectively moisturize and soothe. Canola oil can also be used to treat dry, broken, frizzy hair and split ends. Hot oil treatments are often made with canola oil. It apparently also protects the hair from dirt, pollution and damage from the sun. Canola oil applied to the scalp can also help get rid of dandruff.
CategoryName: Health and Beauty>Bath and Spa>Body and Essential Oils

Title: DèVe Herbes Pure Passion Fruit Oil 15ml (Passiflora Edulis)
Description: Passionfruit Seed Oil, Passiflora incarnata, also known as Passionfruit Oil or Maracuja Oil.Passion fruit oil is full of nutrients that are good for skin. Among these are vitamins A and C, essential fatty acids, copper, magnesium, phosphorus, calcium, and carotenoids. When all these goodies work together, here’s what you get:Anti-aging: Because of the high vitamin C and antioxidant content, passion fruit oil helps slow the damage that leads to the appearance of aging, and also helps preserve collagen and elastin, which keep skin looking firm and youthful.Rejuvenating: Passion fruit oil is also a great source of vitamin A in the form of carotenoids, which is critical for cell growth and repair. A number of phytochemicals in the oil help the body produce vitamin A, which also helps reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.Plumping: A high content of fatty acids like linoleic and oleic acids “feed” the skin what it needs to maintain its structure, keeping skin smooth and plump looking and helping to fend off the appearance of fine lines.Hydrating: This oil is light and non-greasy, and the skin drinks it up quick. It’s the perfect moisturizer for all skin types, and works well for acne-prone skin as well because of its non-clogging moisturizing action.Calming: Like most plant-sourced ingredients, passion fruit oil has an anti-inflammatory property. This may also help reduce swelling and irritation.This oil can also be used as a massage oil helping to ease the pain of arthritic joints and muscle pain.Applying this oil to the scalp is reported to help a variety of concerns from dandruff, itchy scalp, dry scalp and dry, damaged hair. An application to the cuticles of Maracuja Oil helps alleviate dry cuticles and also helps strengthen weak, fragile nails.Passionfruit Seed Oil, Passiflora incarnata, also known as Passionfruit Oil or Maracuja Oil.Passion fruit oil is full of nutrients that are good for skin.
